      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING CHOI (3) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at Geelong over 400m behind Smiling Lily (23.69) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Better than last start and worth following up. HYLAND AZULA (4) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 0.8 lengths (16.83) at this track. Harder here but expected to measure up. OUR ALAMO (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by one length at Traralgon in a handy 20.37 beating Paw Waldo. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can continue on with his winning form. HOLLYWOOD FRANKY (2) is back from a break and worth including.",
